OL,3,CFormer Jersey police officer arrested
OL,4,Cfor sexual assault
OL,6,FA former Jersey police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of assault
OL,8,Fand sexual assault.
OL,10,FThe unnamed man was brought to the
OL,11,FStates of Jersey Police Headquarters
OL,12,Fin St Helier on Monday 11 May and has
OL,13,Fsince been released as investigations
OL,14,Fcontinue.
OL,16,FNo charges have been filed against him.
