OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1778699495
OL,3,CFormer Jersey police officer arrested
OL,4,Cfor sexual assault
OL,6,FIn a statement, the force said:
OL,7,F"States of Jersey Police can confirm
OL,8,Fthat a man was arrested on Monday 11
OL,9,FMay in connection with allegations of
OL,10,Fassault and sexual assault.
OL,12,F"The individual has been released
OL,13,Fpending further enquiries, and no
OL,14,Fcharges have been made at this stage.
OL,16,F"We can confirm the individual is not
OL,17,Fa serving police officer. This is an
OL,18,Fongoing investigation, and it would be
OL,19,Finappropriate to comment any further.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
